data.description: ***$25,000 Price Improvement!***    Located on a quiet street in sought after Reids Prospect /Colgan HS district, this beautiful end unit has been meticulously maintained by one owner and is Move In Ready! With approximately 2500 sf of finished living space on 3 levels, and 35K in seller updates, you will love this open, bright end unit floor plan.  Features include brand new carpet and fresh paint throughout,  beautiful hardwood floors in the huge chef's kitchen with granite countertops, stainless appliances, a center island, and a  bay window. The kitchen flows  into the living room which is wired for surround sound - perfect for gathering to watch football games! Upstairs, the expanded primary suite has 2 huge walk in closets and a relaxing spa like bathroom with corner jetted tub.   2 gar garage, large private fenced back yard , newer composite deck with stairs down to the peaceful patio make this home perfect for entertaining  *Home Warranty paid for by seller will transfer to buyer at closing Recent updates:  HVAC (2019) Washer & Dryer (2020) Carpet (2023) Dishwasher (2023) Garbage disposal (2023) Painted (2023)
